Module hanyaeger.api

Package com.github.hanyaeger.api.engine.entities.entity.collisions

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    Collided
    A Collided represents an non-rotatable YaegerEntity that can be collided with by a Collider.
    Collider
    A Collider represents an YaegerEntity that can be collided with by a Collided
    SideAwareCollided
    A SideAwareCollided represents an YaegerEntity that can be collided with by a Collider and that is aware of which of its side the Collider had collided with.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    CollisionDelegate
    A CollisionDelegate handles all behavior related to Object collisions.
  • Enum Summary 
    Enum Description
    CollisionSide
    A CollisionSide denotes the side of the Collided with which the Collider has collided.
